# SBU 0.4.0 Roadmap
- Add --view-config option to output the configuration of jobs.
- Add --set-interval and --set-retention options to update config of jobs.
- Change --days-to-keep to --retention.
- Change --stop and --restart function to wait until the job is idle before killing processes, --force option will kill without waiting.
- Create upgrade script.
- Create --import and --export functions for migrating jobs.
